40
00:04:06,225 --> 00:04:09,647
And, you all happen to be the witness, right?

41
00:04:09,647 --> 00:04:10,747
Yeah.

42
00:04:10,747 --> 00:04:13,247
Geez, what're you doing back in Kamakura again?

43
00:04:13,247 --> 00:04:15,047
Just sightseeing. Sightseeing!

44
00:04:15,047 --> 00:04:17,047
These kids said they wanted to watch the hydrangeas.

45
00:04:17,047 --> 00:04:19,347
Inspector Yokomizo, may I have a moment with you?

46
