Yeah, according to autopsy, his time of death is around...

60
00:04:58,447 --> 00:05:00,547
Hey! Shut up about that!

61
00:05:00,547 --> 00:05:01,847
Yes, sir.

62
00:05:01,847 --> 00:05:05,047
So, the time of death is around 6:00?

63
