70
00:05:23,947 --> 00:05:25,747
Oh, that's right.

71
00:05:25,747 --> 00:05:28,047
I also kept the stub of my air ticket.

72
00:05:28,047 --> 00:05:30,309
Here you are.

73
00:05:32,311 --> 00:05:33,847
I see.

74
00:05:33,847 --> 00:05:36,047
-Check this out. -Roger.

75
00:05:36,047 --> 00:05:39,547
By the way, did Hisaemon live here alone?

76
00:05:39,547 --> 00:05:42,747
Yeah. He used have servants here looking after him,

77
00:05:42,747 --> 00:05:46,047
