83
00:05:59,747 --> 00:06:04,647
That's right, they may know something about the case.

84
00:06:04,647 --> 00:06:08,647
Well, I don't know if they'd tell the truth though.

85
00:06:11,147 --> 00:06:13,947
Hey, we know you're in there.

86
00:06:13,947 --> 00:06:15,347
