92
00:06:30,647 --> 00:06:32,747
You guys still at it?

93
00:06:32,747 --> 00:06:35,147
Yeah.

94
00:06:35,147 --> 00:06:36,375
-Let's get home! -What?

95
00:06:36,375 --> 00:06:37,947
Just go!

96
00:06:42,747 --> 00:06:43,947
Mr. Yaguchi!

97
00:06:43,947 --> 00:06:45,747
Mr. Akihiko Yaguchi.

98
00:06:45,747 --> 00:06:48,387
This is the police! We want to talk to you.

99
00:06:50,389 --> 00:06:52,391
"Akihiko Yaguchi (37) Second-born Son"

100
00:06:52,391 --> 00:06:54,947
