145
00:09:04,247 --> 00:09:06,847
No! I'm not a greenhorn!

146
00:09:08,527 --> 00:09:10,847
It's the truth. Please believe me!

147
00:09:10,847 --> 00:09:14,147
After that, I went to see my brother Akihiko.

148
00:09:15,247 --> 00:09:18,547
Well? How'd it go?

149
00:09:18,547 --> 00:09:20,547
Dad caught me stealing.

150
00:09:20,547 --> 00:09:21,647
You moron!

151
00:09:21,647 --> 00:09:24,247
I even worked out the plan on how to do it!

152
00:09:24,247 --> 00:09:25,347
Worked out the plan?

153
00:09:25,347 --> 00:09:27,247
What I saw wasn't what we expected at all!

154
00:09:27,247 --> 00:09:29,347
Dad's safe was so sturdy, there was no way to...

