174
00:10:23,947 --> 00:10:25,847
Yeah, of course.

175
00:10:25,847 --> 00:10:30,047
Afterwards, you went to a discount shop nearby to buy some items?

176
00:10:31,147 --> 00:10:34,147
A crowbar, an electric drill.

177
00:10:34,147 --> 00:10:37,447
A number of witnesses confirmed this for us.

178
00:10:37,447 --> 00:10:39,547
I remembered, too.

179
00:10:39,547 --> 00:10:41,747
Look at your right hand.

180
00:10:41,747 --> 00:10:44,623
This is...

181
00:10:44,847 --> 00:10:46,947
Fine, I did come to steal.

182
00:10:46,947 --> 00:10:49,047
But I didn't kill dad!

183
00:10:49,047 --> 00:10:50,629
When I arrived, dad was already...

184
00:10:52,147 --> 00:10:54,247
What the...

