00:11:36,675 --> 00:11:39,147
After seeing the culprit wielding a rifle before his eyes,

200
00:11:39,147 --> 00:11:41,647
why didn't he try to escape?

201
00:11:41,647 --> 00:11:45,447
And then the white crystalline substance.

202
00:11:47,347 --> 00:11:49,647
Just what was that, anyway?

203
00:11:59,138 --> 00:12:00,699
Now then.

204
00:12:00,699 --> 00:12:03,038
Aside from the body,

205
00:12:03,038 --> 00:12:05,038
what else do you notice?

206
00:12:05,038 --> 00:12:07,238
Is something missing?

207
00:12:08,707 --> 00:12:10,038
Now that you mention it...

208
00:12:10,038 --> 00:12:11,538
Oh, yes.

209
00:12:11,538 --> 00:12:14,238
Dad's antique collections are gone!

210
00:12:14,238 --> 00:12:15,438
Yeah.

211
00:12:15,438 --> 00:12:18,738
Faugh. I'd bet it was our older brother that snatched them, right?

212
00:12:18,738 --> 00:12:20,138
What'd you say?

213
00:12:20,138 --> 00:12:23,738
I bet you stole them when you come to break into the safe!

214
00:12:23,738 --> 00:12:29,138
The victim recently discontinued financial aid for his sons.

215
00:12:29,138 --> 00:12:32,238
He also dismissed his servants six months ago.

216
00:12:32,238 --> 00:12:35,338
And then his antiques were gone.

217
00:12:35,338 --> 00:12:36,735
Could it be...

218
00:12:36,735 --> 00:12:39,138
Then, that safe is...

219
00:12:40,739 --> 00:12:45,038
By the way, we found this item in this room.

220
00:12:45,038 --> 00:12:48,038
