221
00:12:48,038 --> 00:12:50,438
Who planted that thing?

222
00:12:50,438 --> 00:12:52,438
You're a pro when it comes to cameras, big bro?

223
00:12:52,438 --> 00:12:53,638
What's this?

224
00:12:53,638 --> 00:12:55,238
Are you saying I did that?

225
00:12:55,238 --> 00:12:56,538
Inspector.

226
00:12:58,038 --> 00:12:59,538
I see.

227
00:12:59,538 --> 00:13:02,538
Everyone, we've come cross further information,

228
00:13:02,538 --> 00:13:04,538
so please come back over to other room again.

