00:13:04,538 --> 00:13:06,238
By the way, officer.

230
00:13:06,238 --> 00:13:08,767
Can you open that safe for us?

231
00:13:08,767 --> 00:13:10,769
Can you try something?

232
00:13:13,438 --> 00:13:15,338
This?

233
00:13:15,338 --> 00:13:16,775
