234
00:13:21,838 --> 00:13:24,138
-Say, Mr. officer. -What?

235
00:13:24,138 --> 00:13:27,138
Where was that stuffed eagle originally?

236
00:13:27,138 --> 00:13:30,538
Let's see. Right over there.

237
00:13:30,538 --> 00:13:32,538
See that dust mark?

238
00:13:32,538 --> 00:13:34,793
I think the eagle was placed here.

239
00:13:34,793 --> 00:13:38,797
And fell off while the victim was struggling with the culprit?

240
00:13:39,738 --> 00:13:42,801
Rokurou, I have received a report

241
00:13:42,801 --> 00:13:44,803
from the Tokushima Police Department.

242
00:13:44,803 --> 00:13:48,807
How was it? I was in Tokushima staying at a hotel, right?

243
00:13:49,038 --> 00:13:51,638
Well, it was witnessed that a man

244
00:13:51,638 --> 00:13:54,138
wearing a hat and sunglasses like yours was there.

245
00:13:54,138 --> 00:13:56,538
Yeah, you mean me.

246
00:13:56,538 --> 00:13:58,838
Well, how should I know?

247
00:13:58,838 --> 00:14:01,638
