253
00:14:14,538 --> 00:14:15,738
No way.

254
00:14:15,738 --> 00:14:19,538
Also, that guest's checkout time was until tomorrow.

255
00:14:19,538 --> 00:14:23,238
But he suddenly decided to leave this morning, I heard.

256
00:14:23,238 --> 00:14:27,838
Perhaps he already knew that Hisaemon was dead at that time.

257
00:14:27,838 --> 00:14:31,638
This morning in a haste, that must be it.

258
00:14:31,638 --> 00:14:34,853
The loans you borrowed were huge.

259
00:14:34,853 --> 00:14:37,838
However, you said you had already secured a way

260
00:14:37,838 --> 00:14:40,538
