261
00:14:40,538 --> 00:14:43,238
-That's... -So big bro, you really did kill dad?

262
00:14:43,238 --> 00:14:44,238
Absolutely no!

263
00:14:44,238 --> 00:14:45,738
So, the person who went to Tokushima

264
00:14:45,738 --> 00:14:48,867
